{"tid":2416712,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國監獄網軍獎勵標準曝光！ 10萬分減（刑）半年","createTime":"2021-02-21T09:24:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-23T12:04:31.000Z","uid":337052,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"820f85f0ac33af0f2d1874b2d6e5db6809f41c9e","tid":2416712,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T09:24:27.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">中國監獄網軍獎勵標準曝光！ 網酸︰「小粉紅」要反省智商</span></strong><br />\n   <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2021/02/21/3445114_1_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2021%2F02%2F21%2F3445114_1_1.jpg&h=1b4d5fa5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國監獄培訓囚犯網軍的現場照片。（翻攝自微信）<br />\n<br />\n2021/02/21 17:12<br />\n〔編譯陳成良／綜合報導〕中國各地監獄中存在大量俗稱「五毛」網軍的網路評論員，已是公開秘密，近年中媒曾發表大量「正能量報導」，透露全國多個監獄培訓「服刑人員網絡（網路）評論員」的情況。<span class=\"red\">近日網上傳出中國監獄對囚犯網軍的獎分標準，顯示這批「監獄五毛」製造了大量網路垃圾。</span>在海外社交媒體，網友呼籲被網軍欺騙的老少「粉紅」要反省一下自己的智商。<br />\n<br />\n2月17日，中國網媒《網易新聞》刊出《每個服刑人員都在努力地攢分》相關報導，有疑似知情網友在底下留言，透露了部分中國監獄給囚犯網軍的獎分標準：「<span class=\"red\">發帖（發文）3分，跟貼（在發表的帖子後面，寫上自己的意見）1分，10萬分減（刑）半年。</span>」<br />\n<br />\n該獎勵標準類似一般網軍「發帖5毛」的物質獎勵，因此引發關注。在推特，有網友發文稱，「老少粉紅是不是要反省一下自己的智商，你們被一群『爭取自由』的囚犯給騙了」。<br />\n<br />\n有網友計算，<span class=\"red\">如果要減刑半年，則需「跟帖」10萬，或者「發帖」逾3萬篇</span>，不禁感嘆，熱切盼望減刑的囚犯會替中國製造多少垃圾網文。<br />\n<br />\n「小粉紅」初期用來稱呼在中國偏向民族主義的網友，2010年後網上湧入許多偏向民族主義的中國青年，部分媒體譬喻小粉紅為「現代紅衛兵」。小粉紅會透過翻牆在網上攻擊與辱罵意見相反的人，經常過度檢視他人行為並過度解釋「辱華」一詞。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2021/02/21/3445114_2_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2021%2F02%2F21%2F3445114_2_1.jpg&h=f07ae4a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網易新聞發文《每個服刑人員都在努力地攢分》（左），在留言區有疑似知情網友，透露部分中國監獄給囚犯網軍的獎分標準。（取自網路）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3445114\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3445114&d=0FWZMlR46yIxX%2BJDTULvnS3IRifvRw8PV%2BxDOhj55DY%3D&h=358c1235\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3445114&h=1b9f43a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3445114</a>"},{"pid":"3185b047377b2ca43b2115d13edbca03ae6f0110","tid":2416712,"uid":149844,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T09:26:41.000Z","msg":"坐監都有得上網<br />\n好過香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又贏"},{"pid":"eecb3774f9262e2fabb4a7052ed66c83e7479bc3","tid":2416712,"uid":321002,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T09:27:33.000Z","msg":"NMSL，又得1分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0593532f617b99601b6a661608b6db7dc93c9b04","tid":2416712,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3185b047377b2ca43b2115d13edbca03ae6f0110","tid":2416712,"uid":149844,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T09:26:41.000Z","msg":"坐監都有得上網<br />\n好過香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又贏"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T09:27:50.000Z","msg":"說不定還可以上FB和IG"},{"pid":"a49f172a894ced82421a3b17e13aababaa5e6c04","tid":2416712,"uid":271857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T09:29:58.000Z","msg":"起來做我的奴隸的人民?"},{"pid":"0f5ed9b77289b44a741b9d9eb2f56090785d7577","tid":2416712,"uid":149844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0593532f617b99601b6a661608b6db7dc93c9b04","tid":2416712,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3185b047377b2ca43b2115d13edbca03ae6f0110","tid":2416712,"uid":149844,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T09:26:41.000Z","msg":"坐監都有得